{"tid":1513011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★天意？】大埔廣福道墮簷篷石屎　擊中賣買旗男女 兩人送院治理","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T07:23:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1316793e7463cc672362bfdc77025d8a37fea89","tid":1513011,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"早上10時許，大埔廣福道107號一幅有逾50年樓齡大廈，疑風雨後簷篷石屎剝落，面積約15乘30厘米，擊中正在樓底下的兩名男女，分別頭及手受傷，仍清醒。據悉，留在地上最大塊的石屎有15乘15厘米。<br />\n<br />\n被擊中男子姓鄧( 33歲)，頭部受傷，據悉，他正陪同外娚在街上賣旗籌款，涉事被擊中的老婦姓黃（76歲）手部受傷，疑因付出愛心買旗時無辜被石屎擊中；兩人 清醒送大埔那打素醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2438654/大埔廣福道墮簷篷石屎%E3%80%80擊中賣買旗善心男女送院治理?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2438654%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%BB%A3%E7%A6%8F%E9%81%93%E5%A2%AE%E7%B0%B7%E7%AF%B7%E7%9F%B3%E5%B1%8E%25E3%2580%2580%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%A3%E8%B2%B7%E6%97%97%E5%96%84%E5%BF%83%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5EBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=5d42e23c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2438654/大埔廣福道墮簷篷石屎%E3%80%80擊中賣買旗善心男女送院治理?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"71d094aace0ae37e3a8031376a2e9fa22a316861","tid":1513011,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5EBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=df9834e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br /